The paper proposes a novel multi-agent transfer learning framework that improves the learning efficiency of multi-agent systems. The paper discusses the use of deep RL approaches and proposes a new option learning algorithm. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also discusses the dynamics of the environment and rewards, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
